author: rockiger
title: As a user I want to filter my currrent list for project, that I can concentrate on one.

author: rockiger
title: As a User I want to add recurring task, that I can track task, that I have to do often.

author: rockiger
title: As a User I want to have an intelligent Entry-Box for the a new task, that I can add important meta information like due date, projecet, etc. easily.

author: rockiger
title: AS a user I want that Akiee restores the state right where I left it, that I can pick up my work where I left it.

author: rockiger
title: As a user I want to change the ranking/order of a task via drag and drop, that I can less cumberstone with ranking.

author: rockiger
title: As a user I want to keep notes (not tasks), that I want to keep for future reference, that I can remember important information.

author: rockiger
title: When I work an different computers, I want to sync my files via a cloud drive service, therefore I need a possibility to change the location of my task file.

author: rockiger
title: As A User I want to see the details of a task when I klick on it, that I can see notes I did to finish it.

author: rockiger
title: As a (kanban) user I want to have the DONE state ordered by time in reverse, that I can see what I finished last

author: rockiger
title: As a  user, I want better integration, that the app feels more native to me.

author: rockiger
title: As a developer I want to explore the options of using Clojurescript for Akiee, that I can leverage Lisp for competitive advantage

author: rockiger
title: Search- and Entry-Box can both be open at the same time.

title: If I change a task in the Kanban board the view switches to the state of that changed task.
